1
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,360
Zhou?

2
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,340
You finally made it.

3
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,159
What did he tell you?

4
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,219
Case progress.

5
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,139
I'll go see him the day after.

6
00:02:29,219 --> 00:02:30,400
We'll both go see him.

7
00:02:34,379 --> 00:02:35,319
It was closed as an accident

8
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,479
a while back.

9
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:37,939
Now there's new progress.

10
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,240
They suspect it was arson

11
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,979
by a former employee of Company Kuang.

12
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,780
They wanted to use it to fish for Zhang Bin,

13
00:02:42,780 --> 00:02:43,460
so they kept it quiet.

14
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:46,259
You go.

15
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:49,419
Come back.

16
00:02:53,979 --> 00:02:54,500
What?

17
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:56,419
Nothing.

18
00:03:09,340 --> 00:03:09,819
Let's go.

19
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:23,900
Faster.

20
00:03:24,979 --> 00:03:25,460
Faster.

21
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,020
Run faster.

22
00:03:33,539 --> 00:03:34,180
What's wrong?

23
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:36,419
What?

24
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,500
Cops.

25
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,419
Keep an eye on him.

26
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,500
How's it going?

27
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:53,680
Cops are here.

28
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:54,439
Where...

29
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,300
Which way?

30
00:04:00,819 --> 00:04:01,500
They're not plainclothes?

31
00:04:02,219 --> 00:04:03,319
No idea.

32
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,300
If you hadn't been so impulsive,

33
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,340
we wouldn't be

34
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:11,199
in this mess.

35
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,479
What did you say?

36
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:14,879
That's because Hu was provoked.

37
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,699
If you ask me,

38
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,899
Zhang Bin's a real jerk.

39
00:04:19,019 --> 00:04:19,399
We're

40
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,839
out here like stray dogs.

41
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,939
But him?

42
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,220
Things have come to this.

43
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,000
We can't go back to the site.

44
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,939
What's the point of all this talk?

45
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,420
Figure something out.

46
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,339
If only Zhai were still here.

47
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:46,399
Sit down.

48
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,579
Keep it low-key.

49
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,480
Mr. Zhang heard

50
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,459
you and Mr. Chen

51
00:04:54,459 --> 00:04:55,300
have some misunderstanding.

52
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,620
We're all friends.

53
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,120
Why make it so ugly?

54
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,199
He still owes us money.

55
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,620
Who's friends with him?

56
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,180
What are you doing?

57
00:05:04,819 --> 00:05:06,160
I know you guys are laying low.

58
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,360
Mr. Zhang

59
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,899
doesn't want to pursue anything.

60
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,959
The early severance of 160,000,

61
00:05:13,259 --> 00:05:14,060
with 3%

62
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,199
bank interest.

63
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:17,240
Here's 180,000 in cash.

64
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,480
There's a catch?

65
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,920
Now you're being distant.

66
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,300
You just need to

67
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:30,579
do one last favor for Mr. Zhang.

68
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:45,459
Ms. Miao, morning.

69
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:46,720
- Jing, morning.
- Jing, morning.

70
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,259
Morning.

71
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:11,519
Come in.

72
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:13,839
Hello.

73
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,139
I'm from the audit team.

74
00:06:15,379 --> 00:06:16,019
I'm here to pick up

75
00:06:16,019 --> 00:06:17,360
the contract for the freight department.

76
00:06:18,459 --> 00:06:19,100
Let me check.

77
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:23,879
I don't see

78
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,259
the approval for the access request.

79
00:06:26,339 --> 00:06:26,860
Our director

80
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:28,139
already submitted it.

81
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,360
Maybe it's still going through

82
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,079
the process?

83
00:06:33,579 --> 00:06:34,920
Then we'll have to wait for approval.

84
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:36,220
The process hasn't reached me yet.

85
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,399
I can't just hand them over.

86
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,439
We need them urgently for the team.

87
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:39,560
How about I take them for now?

88
00:06:40,759 --> 00:06:41,639
Let me call my supervisor

89
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:42,120
and ask.

90
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,480
It goes through the freight department.

91
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,060
Should be Mr. Chen in charge.

92
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:47,839
You can call him.

93
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,079
Hello, Mr. Chen.

94
00:06:58,540 --> 00:06:59,620
I have someone from

95
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,459
the audit team here...

96
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,199
Ms. Miao.

97
00:07:01,699 --> 00:07:03,120
Ms. Miao from the audit team

98
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,860
wants the freight contracts.

99
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,959
Did you approve the process on your end?

100
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,279
One moment.

101
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:10,439
I see it.

102
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:11,220
No problem.

103
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,399
Alright.

104
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:14,579
One moment, please.

105
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,500
Toy.

106
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,220
Jing.

107
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,060
Mr. Cen wants you to go see him.

108
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,679
Come in.

109
00:08:39,139 --> 00:08:39,720
Care for a game?

110
00:08:58,039 --> 00:08:58,740
That aggressive?

111
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,539
Taking risky moves.

112
00:09:01,419 --> 00:09:02,940
But you can't ignore the consequences.

113
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,779
Did the archives department ask you?

114
00:09:07,379 --> 00:09:07,879
I managed

115
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:08,919
to backfill the process for you.

116
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,299
But being that reckless

117
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,759
isn't like you.

118
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,919
If I'd told you,

119
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,580
you would've told me to be careful.

120
00:09:15,899 --> 00:09:16,840
Now that it's done,

121
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:18,419
you've got to clean it up for me.

122
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,779
It's not exactly above board,

123
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,519
but it's

124
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,799
the fastest way.

125
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,580
I know it's a procedural violation.

126
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:27,379
But I had my reasons

127
00:09:27,379 --> 00:09:28,440
for doing it.

128
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,019
You've said it all, haven't you?

129
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,120
I'll file a violation report.

130
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:34,340
Dock my pay if you have to.

131
00:09:35,899 --> 00:09:36,740
I didn't call you in

132
00:09:37,539 --> 00:09:38,580
just to hold you accountable.

133
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,100
They've been hiding

134
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:42,320
a deficit in their books.

135
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,539
But because the cash flow looked fine,

136
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:45,759
it went unnoticed

137
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,820
for years.

138
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:49,399
I checked the raw data.

139
00:09:49,779 --> 00:09:52,039
That deficit started the year

140
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:52,919
Hongshen Investment

141
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,440
turned from loss to profit.

142
00:09:57,220 --> 00:09:58,120
But that's normal.

143
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,460
Robbing Peter to pay Paul, you know.

144
00:10:01,139 --> 00:10:02,399
High turnover can't stop.

145
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,100
But now Hongshen's going public.

146
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,519
If Haoyun has problems

147
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,259
at this critical moment,

148
00:10:09,139 --> 00:10:10,200
Hongshen will come down hard,

149
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,720
maybe even

150
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,440
cut losses and pull out.

151
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:16,460
That would cripple Haoyun.

152
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:19,259
So

153
00:10:19,899 --> 00:10:21,539
Zhang Bin will find a way

154
00:10:21,779 --> 00:10:22,639
to cover this shortfall.

155
00:10:23,539 --> 00:10:25,120
Haoyun started out as Company Kuang.

156
00:10:25,539 --> 00:10:26,960
Zhang Bin got the funding

157
00:10:27,059 --> 00:10:28,559
to build it up to Haoyun's scale.

158
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:30,899
Zhang Bin wants to open

159
00:10:30,899 --> 00:10:31,879
a new transport route.

160
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:34,100
But that route isn't clean.

161
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:35,980
The police are already suspicious

162
00:10:36,179 --> 00:10:36,659
and watching closely.

163
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:38,980
So

164
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,399
he has to take a risk

165
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,720
and shift the blame.

166
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:45,340
So

167
00:10:46,419 --> 00:10:47,940
even if they find who set the fire,

168
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,419
they won't be able to

169
00:10:49,419 --> 00:10:50,639
link it to Haoyun at all.

170
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,080
Right.

171
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,240
There's no hard evidence yet.

172
00:10:54,659 --> 00:10:56,440
And since it involves Gangcheng businesses,

173
00:10:56,779 --> 00:10:58,100
the police can't just

174
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,500
get a search warrant on him.

175
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:02,080
All that effort

176
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,679
just to balance the books?

177
00:11:04,179 --> 00:11:04,980
That doesn't add up.

178
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,279
Sounds like

179
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,519
you already have a plan.

180
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:17,500
Which team handled the shipments

181
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:18,419
for Baiyou before?

182
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:19,759
Bai and Xu.

183
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,480
Bai

184
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,480
ships small loads

185
00:11:21,559 --> 00:11:22,279
to Gangcheng.

186
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,559
Xu does big commercial hauls.

187
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,379
Ships nationwide.

188
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:27,940
Where's Bai?

189
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,580
The schedule says he's on the road today.

190
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:32,480
He took the day off.

191
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,240
I'm covering for him.

192
00:11:36,379 --> 00:11:36,639
Right.

193
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,899
Bai's been taking a lot of time off.

194
00:11:37,899 --> 00:11:39,279
He's missed quite a few shifts.

195
00:11:39,419 --> 00:11:39,960
A few

196
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,940
of the veteran drivers

197
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:41,840
have been out too.

198
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,120
But we got a few new faces.

199
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,580
Quite a few replacements.

200
00:11:47,419 --> 00:11:48,659
Bai's not feeling well.

201
00:11:48,679 --> 00:11:49,460
He'll be in this afternoon.

202
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:50,840
I don't know about the others.

203
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:55,600
No shipments tonight.

204
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:56,899
You've only done three trips

205
00:11:56,899 --> 00:11:58,000
with these small loads.

206
00:11:58,539 --> 00:11:59,860
No other dispatch arrangements?

207
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,000
Not really.

208
00:12:01,139 --> 00:12:02,519
That's how the company set it up.

209
00:12:03,379 --> 00:12:03,740
Oh,

210
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,620
the drivers are free,

211
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,460
but the trucks aren't.

212
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:06,720
Mr. Tao recently brought in

213
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,299
some new drivers.

214
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,059
Probably handed the trucks over to them.

215
00:12:14,019 --> 00:12:14,980
New drivers?

216
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:16,220
Yes.

217
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:45,340
I suspect

218
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:47,679
the new route Zhang Bin wants to open

219
00:12:48,059 --> 00:12:48,960
involves smuggling.

220
00:12:53,059 --> 00:12:54,240
After the team pulls out,

221
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:56,019
I'll stay in Vineton under the guise

222
00:12:56,179 --> 00:12:57,279
of wrapping things up.

223
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:00,539
Yi.

224
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,460
Come on.

225
00:13:02,659 --> 00:13:03,179
Try some.

226
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,820
Just brought this back

227
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:05,460
from Gangcheng.

228
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,759
This can't be found in Vineton now.

229
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:20,759
Hand-pulled noodles.

230
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:22,519
Old-school.

231
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:26,139
Tastes just like that roast goose stall

232
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,059
on Huaihua Street

233
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,220
back then.

234
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:30,279
Eat up.

235
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,480
What's wrong, Yi?

236
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,220
It does taste like Huaihua Street.

237
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,440
Why have you been missing so much work?

238
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:04,860
I've

239
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,120
had stomach issues for a while.

240
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,139
Been to the hospital a few times.

241
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,519
See,

242
00:14:10,659 --> 00:14:11,960
I even forgot my meds today.

243
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:15,519
Let me go grab my pills.

244
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,320
You go ahead and eat.

245
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,159
Hold on.

246
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:18,100
Where's the medicine?

247
00:14:18,179 --> 00:14:18,720
I'll get it for you.

248
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,460
In my truck.

249
00:14:22,879 --> 00:14:24,080
In the red bag.

250
00:14:25,059 --> 00:14:25,519
Okay.

251
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:26,460
Wait here.

252
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:27,700
Thanks, Yi.

253
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:40,980
Here.

254
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:42,700
Thanks, Yi.

255
00:14:44,740 --> 00:14:45,059
Haven't...

256
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,220
Haven't I done enough runs this month?

257
00:14:48,799 --> 00:14:49,220
Not really.

258
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:51,059
It's just that a few new drivers

259
00:14:51,059 --> 00:14:51,820
don't know the rules.

260
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,779
One guy handled the Baiyou No. 4 shipment.

261
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:55,139
Almost messed it up.

262
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,919
Small loads aren't ours.

263
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,220
We only ever deliver

264
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:01,360
No. 7 goods to the dock.

265
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:02,200
All other numbers

266
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,580
go through large freight.

267
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,860
No. 7?

268
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:21,279
Like this?

269
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:24,919
Yi,

270
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,720
I didn't steal this.

271
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,399
It fell out from under

272
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,179
the pallet.

273
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,360
I found it when I was closing up

274
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,259
the truck.

275
00:15:35,539 --> 00:15:37,919
It wasn't dirty or damaged,

276
00:15:39,559 --> 00:15:40,500
so I thought I'd take it home

277
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,220
for my daughter.

278
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:46,879
Where's your medicine?

279
00:15:59,399 --> 00:16:00,240
Finished it.

280
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,080
Forgot to get a refill.

281
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:04,120
Yi,

282
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:04,799
I...

283
00:16:04,899 --> 00:16:06,240
I'll try to do more runs next month.

284
00:16:07,259 --> 00:16:08,299
I didn't say I'm firing you.

285
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:10,840
It's already opened.

286
00:16:11,139 --> 00:16:12,100
I'll write it off as damaged later.

287
00:16:12,779 --> 00:16:14,139
Th-thanks, Yi.

288
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,340
When did you get stomach issues?

289
00:16:17,139 --> 00:16:18,299
You were fine before.

290
00:16:19,700 --> 00:16:20,759
About three or four months ago.

291
00:16:21,779 --> 00:16:23,500
And I've got diabetes.

292
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,200
So I can't just eat anything.

293
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,259
Is there anyone else

294
00:16:30,580 --> 00:16:31,139
in your crew

295
00:16:31,139 --> 00:16:32,179
feeling unwell?

296
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:42,940
Nothing serious.

297
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:45,919
Some of the guys

298
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:46,980
just had

299
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,000
headaches

300
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,340
and lost their appetite.

301
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,139
Because everyone's been doing

302
00:16:51,139 --> 00:16:52,419
a lot of night runs lately.

303
00:16:53,379 --> 00:16:54,379
It's pretty much the same

304
00:16:55,039 --> 00:16:56,259
for all of us.

305
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:11,980
Let's go to the hospital.

306
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:18,680
Bai Guoqiang, right?

307
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:20,680
This is your bed.

308
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,440
Here's your hospital gown.

309
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,299
You can

310
00:17:23,299 --> 00:17:24,859
go change now.

311
00:17:25,099 --> 00:17:25,640
There's a call button

312
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:26,519
by the bed.

313
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:27,180
Ring

314
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:28,559
if you need anything.

315
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:29,680
Alright.

316
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:30,420
Thank you.

317
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:35,339
Have you contacted your family?

318
00:17:37,559 --> 00:17:39,079
My daughter's only in elementary school.

319
00:17:39,619 --> 00:17:40,940
Someone's got to take care of her at home.

320
00:17:41,259 --> 00:17:42,680
My wife's got an early shift tomorrow.

321
00:17:43,079 --> 00:17:44,740
It's just indigestion.

322
00:17:45,279 --> 00:17:46,740
I don't need to stay in the hospital.

323
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:01,900
What's that on your back?

324
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:06,359
Just some rashes.

325
00:18:07,019 --> 00:18:08,039
I put some liniment on them.

326
00:18:08,859 --> 00:18:09,619
It's been over half a month,

327
00:18:09,619 --> 00:18:10,339
but they haven't cleared up.

328
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:13,220
They haven't gone away

329
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:14,700
and you didn't come to the hospital?

330
00:18:17,119 --> 00:18:18,740
We drive day and night.

331
00:18:19,059 --> 00:18:20,660
Eat and sleep in the truck.

332
00:18:21,339 --> 00:18:22,759
Never have the time.

333
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:26,000
I'll go check the results with the doctor.

334
00:18:42,779 --> 00:18:43,579
Since your company

335
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,839
does transport,

336
00:18:45,759 --> 00:18:46,740
why aren't you using proper protection

337
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,559
when moving hazardous materials?

338
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:50,839
Here, take a look.

339
00:18:52,299 --> 00:18:53,920
White blood cell and platelet counts

340
00:18:54,339 --> 00:18:55,980
are both below normal.

341
00:19:03,759 --> 00:19:04,779
What's his condition?

342
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,019
He

343
00:19:06,039 --> 00:19:07,539
already has diabetes.

344
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:09,319
Based on these readings,

345
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:10,839
he's been exposed

346
00:19:10,839 --> 00:19:11,740
for at least a month.

347
00:19:13,019 --> 00:19:14,220
Are you sure that's the cause?

348
00:19:14,539 --> 00:19:15,680
The rest of the crew

349
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,740
don't seem to be reacting much.

350
00:19:18,059 --> 00:19:18,859
Well,

351
00:19:19,259 --> 00:19:20,119
his

352
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,200
white blood cells were already low.

353
00:19:23,279 --> 00:19:24,160
Even if no one else

354
00:19:24,519 --> 00:19:26,440
in the group has issues,

355
00:19:26,579 --> 00:19:28,140
he'd be the first to show symptoms.

356
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,759
He can't wait any longer.

357
00:19:30,079 --> 00:19:31,140
He needs treatment now.

358
00:19:33,779 --> 00:19:34,180
What exactly

359
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,380
is your company transporting?

360
00:19:35,779 --> 00:19:36,579
Don't you know?

361
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:22,259
Can you tell what this is?

362
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,819
Silver-gray.

363
00:20:28,579 --> 00:20:29,720
Metallic luster.

364
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,680
Denser than iron.

365
00:20:33,099 --> 00:20:33,920
If I'm not wrong,

366
00:20:35,019 --> 00:20:36,500
this is germanium.

367
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:42,359
These people

368
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:43,960
have some serious nerve.

369
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:49,019
Can we file a case with this?

370
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:52,200
Physical evidence obtained illegally

371
00:20:52,519 --> 00:20:53,500
can't be used for filing a case.

372
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:54,839
Right.

373
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,680
It would compromise judicial fairness.

374
00:20:57,740 --> 00:20:58,960
Can't use it as grounds for prosecution.

375
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:00,460
What a shame.

376
00:21:02,519 --> 00:21:03,400
I'll take it back

377
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,839
and have our forensics team

378
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:05,819
run proper tests on it.

379
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:08,079
On the bright side,

380
00:21:08,380 --> 00:21:09,380
we're not

381
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,920
completely without evidence now.

382
00:21:12,539 --> 00:21:13,500
All we need

383
00:21:13,819 --> 00:21:14,380
is a chance

384
00:21:14,380 --> 00:21:15,500
to make a formal arrest.

385
00:21:21,259 --> 00:21:21,759
Soon...

386
00:21:29,740 --> 00:21:30,240
Blow-dry my hair.

387
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:43,799
Scoot forward.

388
00:22:01,059 --> 00:22:02,779
When you saw Zhou out,

389
00:22:03,019 --> 00:22:04,200
what did he say to you?

390
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:07,180
I brought him up to speed.

391
00:22:08,099 --> 00:22:09,180
Remember that inventory check

392
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,240
when you rode with me?

393
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:12,380
That's when I noticed

394
00:22:12,519 --> 00:22:13,839
something off with Haoyun's fleet.

395
00:22:15,519 --> 00:22:16,599
I've pretty much figured out

396
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:17,759
how they're running their operation.

397
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:19,720
Bai's truck

398
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,920
is a small one.

399
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:22,599
No big lettering

400
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,079
on the back.

401
00:22:25,519 --> 00:22:26,599
There are two fleets like this.

402
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:27,839
The trucks

403
00:22:27,839 --> 00:22:28,799
are identical.

404
00:22:29,519 --> 00:22:31,579
Let's call them Black and White trucks.

405
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,059
There's a gap between

406
00:22:45,059 --> 00:22:45,940
the checkpoint and the border.

407
00:22:46,539 --> 00:22:47,220
That's where

408
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:47,880
they

409
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,059
pull their switch.

410
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,799
White trucks go into the checkpoint,

411
00:22:59,299 --> 00:23:00,319
black ones take a back road

412
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:01,700
into an abandoned parking lot.

413
00:23:18,019 --> 00:23:18,700
White trucks

414
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:19,880
don't carry any contraband.

415
00:23:20,660 --> 00:23:21,700
The goods are all on the Black ones.

416
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:25,940
So White trucks

417
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,700
clear the checkpoint safely,

418
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:29,920
leaving clean records.

419
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,940
They swap plates there.

420
00:23:33,819 --> 00:23:35,099
So when they come out,

421
00:23:35,619 --> 00:23:36,359
they're already Black trucks

422
00:23:36,359 --> 00:23:37,599
wearing White truck plates.

423
00:23:46,220 --> 00:23:47,259
Those stuffed toys

424
00:23:47,259 --> 00:23:48,700
are how they move the goods.

425
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:50,779
In Gangcheng, I checked that they

426
00:23:50,779 --> 00:23:52,279
only have six production lines

427
00:23:52,279 --> 00:23:53,099
on paper.

428
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:54,900
But toys

429
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:56,200
with the number seven prefix

430
00:23:56,539 --> 00:23:57,740
don't exist on the open market.

431
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,079
They only show up

432
00:23:59,079 --> 00:24:00,759
in Haoyun's transport routes.

433
00:24:01,259 --> 00:24:01,880
That's how they're

434
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:03,000
running their smuggling operation.

435
00:24:09,259 --> 00:24:10,619
Don't frown like Zhou.

436
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:12,319
Relax.

437
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:13,500
They have a plan.

438
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:15,839
Now that

439
00:24:15,839 --> 00:24:16,940
it's handed over to the police,

440
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:17,740
you should

441
00:24:17,740 --> 00:24:18,779
stay out of it.

442
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,240
No more playing the lone hero.

443
00:24:24,319 --> 00:24:24,960
Got it?

444
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:43,420
Lights out.

445
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,079
Bedtime.

446
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,640
You sure know how to settle in.

447
00:24:50,380 --> 00:24:51,880
I've done this before.

448
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,019
The other day

449
00:24:53,019 --> 00:24:54,119
when my sheets weren't dry,

450
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:54,799
I slept right here.

451
00:24:58,599 --> 00:24:59,299
Hurry up.

452
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:23,220
I'm telling you,

453
00:25:23,519 --> 00:25:25,119
when I was in Gangcheng the other day,

454
00:25:25,119 --> 00:25:26,400
I went to so many malls.

455
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:28,480
Cen Ye and I checked every single one.

456
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,440
We were looking for those...

457
00:25:42,519 --> 00:25:43,259
Just sleep.

458
00:26:03,559 --> 00:26:04,160
Sleep.

459
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,140
Bai's sick.

460
00:26:23,539 --> 00:26:24,279
Who's leading us

461
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:25,160
this time?

462
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,180
Who knows.

463
00:26:27,380 --> 00:26:28,119
They won't tell us anything.

464
00:26:28,279 --> 00:26:29,420
Just said to wait.

465
00:26:32,339 --> 00:26:33,000
Why don't you go ask?

466
00:26:34,279 --> 00:26:35,059
Go ask.

467
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,140
- Go on.
- Go on.

468
00:26:42,319 --> 00:26:42,819
Mr. Tao.

469
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,099
Sir.

470
00:26:44,579 --> 00:26:44,900
When

471
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:45,880
are we heading out?

472
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,519
What are we hauling this time?

473
00:26:50,559 --> 00:26:51,440
Just wait.

474
00:26:51,940 --> 00:26:52,420
No questions.

475
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:53,900
Just drive like you always do.

476
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:55,019
Don't mess up the job.

477
00:26:55,319 --> 00:26:55,940
Go on.

478
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,319
Yes.

479
00:27:14,759 --> 00:27:15,359
Tired of waiting?

480
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:19,980
Just wasting time.

481
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:23,859
Who's that?

482
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:31,099
Let's move!

483
00:27:33,599 --> 00:27:34,500
This is the new guy?

484
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:38,000
What a smug prick.

485
00:27:38,099 --> 00:27:38,740
Pfft!

486
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,500
Alright.

487
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:39,940
Stop staring.

488
00:27:40,079 --> 00:27:40,700
Move out!

489
00:27:41,039 --> 00:27:41,740
Alright, let's go.

490
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:42,660
Let's go.

491
00:28:43,519 --> 00:28:44,039
Get out.

492
00:28:44,039 --> 00:28:44,700
Routine inspection.

493
00:28:45,839 --> 00:28:46,519
Open the trunk.

494
00:28:49,019 --> 00:28:50,059
There are

495
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,339
just some toys

496
00:28:52,339 --> 00:28:53,880
in here.

497
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:54,940
Nothing else.

498
00:28:56,740 --> 00:28:57,980
Show me your vehicle registration

499
00:28:58,299 --> 00:28:58,799
and driver's license.

500
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,940
All my documents are in the truck.

501
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,180
Come with me.

502
00:29:15,859 --> 00:29:16,779
Officer,

503
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:17,259
look.

504
00:29:17,259 --> 00:29:19,759
Here's my waybill.

505
00:29:21,299 --> 00:29:22,099
Driver's license.

506
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,480
Vehicle registration.

507
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:26,180
ID card.

508
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:32,400
You're a driver for Haoyun?

509
00:29:33,099 --> 00:29:33,720
Yeah.

510
00:29:34,099 --> 00:29:34,720
That's me.

511
00:29:38,779 --> 00:29:40,500
Stop right there!

512
00:29:44,619 --> 00:29:46,259
It's got nothing to do with me.

513
00:29:46,259 --> 00:29:47,099
Easy there.

514
00:29:47,099 --> 00:29:47,680
Why did you run?

515
00:29:50,079 --> 00:29:50,779
Officer Zhou?

516
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,799
We're old friends.

517
00:29:52,799 --> 00:29:53,400
You?

518
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:55,359
I just

519
00:29:55,359 --> 00:29:56,880
forgot my documents today.

520
00:29:57,079 --> 00:29:57,619
What's in the truck?

521
00:29:57,759 --> 00:29:58,259
Checked it.

522
00:29:58,339 --> 00:29:59,019
Just dolls.

523
00:29:59,160 --> 00:29:59,900
Nothing else.

524
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:03,400
Take him

525
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,259
and the truck in.

526
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:04,799
Yes sir.

527
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:05,420
I...

528
00:30:05,799 --> 00:30:06,359
Officer Zhou,

529
00:30:06,359 --> 00:30:07,380
I'll get them reissued tomorrow.

530
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,000
Alright?

531
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:08,400
Take him away.

532
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:09,599
Officer.

533
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:16,019
Officer Zhou's my friend.

534
00:30:16,539 --> 00:30:18,859
I didn't do this.

535
00:30:19,380 --> 00:30:21,740
Officer, I've been here so many times.

536
00:30:22,279 --> 00:30:22,940
Chen Yi!

537
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:24,500
What are you doing?

538
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:25,420
What do you want?

539
00:30:25,420 --> 00:30:25,940
Don't move!

540
00:30:26,019 --> 00:30:26,619
Stay put!

541
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,420
Mr. Zhai must've been blind.

542
00:30:30,980 --> 00:30:32,559
Zhang Bin got himself a good lapdog!

543
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,099
What are you doing?

544
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,160
Stay put!

545
00:30:38,579 --> 00:30:38,900
Take him inside!

546
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,279
I didn't do anything wrong!

547
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:40,819
Get in there!

548
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:44,480
It's alright.

549
00:30:45,859 --> 00:30:48,440
You two have been going back and forth

550
00:30:48,579 --> 00:30:49,779
between the hospital and here.

551
00:30:50,619 --> 00:30:51,559
Go home and wash off the bad luck

552
00:30:51,559 --> 00:30:52,259
with pomelo leaves.

553
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:54,920
Again with that stuff.

554
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,099
Just listen to me.

555
00:30:57,799 --> 00:30:58,240
Come on.

556
00:31:04,339 --> 00:31:04,880
Take it slow.

557
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:18,559
Although Zhang Bin isn't

558
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,220
directly connected to Sun Hu's case,

559
00:31:20,779 --> 00:31:21,380
we still

560
00:31:22,299 --> 00:31:23,200
need to be careful.

561
00:31:51,460 --> 00:31:51,960
Officer Zhou.

562
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:53,400
I've caused you

563
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,359
a lot of trouble lately.

564
00:31:54,359 --> 00:31:54,779
Thank you.

565
00:31:56,099 --> 00:31:56,819
Just doing my job.

566
00:31:57,420 --> 00:31:58,019
No worries.

567
00:32:04,660 --> 00:32:05,160
Are you alright?

568
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,839
This whole thing

569
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,859
shook them up

570
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:15,900
a bit.

571
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,059
I found a place.

572
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:21,180
I'll take them to shoot some pool later

573
00:32:22,079 --> 00:32:22,680
to unwind.

574
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,319
Officer Zhou,

575
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,279
if you're interested,

576
00:32:26,279 --> 00:32:26,779
you should join us.

577
00:32:28,099 --> 00:32:28,500
No, thanks.

578
00:32:29,579 --> 00:32:30,359
I'm on duty.

579
00:32:30,759 --> 00:32:31,380
Can't really get away.

580
00:32:33,339 --> 00:32:33,920
No pressure.

581
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:36,720
By the way,

582
00:32:38,579 --> 00:32:39,839
it's been unsafe around here lately.

583
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:41,220
Mr. Zhang, you should

584
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:42,799
keep a low profile

585
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:44,619
and avoid going out at night.

586
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:46,140
Don't worry.

587
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,079
I won't cause any trouble

588
00:32:48,079 --> 00:32:48,680
for the police.

589
00:32:53,319 --> 00:32:53,980
Let's go.

590
00:32:54,799 --> 00:32:55,980
You two sit in the back.

591
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,119
Don't just stand there.

592
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:01,920
I put you in the back

593
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:02,940
so we can talk.

594
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:06,859
Li.

595
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:52,039
I'll get my documents

596
00:33:52,039 --> 00:33:52,539
reissued tomorrow.

597
00:33:52,539 --> 00:33:53,079
Alright?

598
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,160
Officer... Officer Zhou?

599
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:56,039
Step out.

600
00:33:56,039 --> 00:33:56,420
Let me handle this.

601
00:33:56,579 --> 00:33:58,059
I didn't do anything wrong.

602
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,019
Tell me about the arson.

603
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,679
Come clean

604
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:15,360
