616
00:35:01,159 --> 00:35:01,900
What a shame.

617
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:06,000
Crime does pay, I guess.‌

618
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,300
Truly a shame.

619
00:35:13,539 --> 00:35:14,579
So what if crime pays?

620
00:35:15,559 --> 00:35:16,519
Once a warrant's out,

621
