626
00:35:31,179 --> 00:35:32,360
You played against her back in the 2000s.

627
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:49,260
I remember.

628
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:51,639
Today,

629
00:35:52,119 --> 00:35:53,300
I just want you two

630
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,119
to relax and have some fun.

631
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:56,920
There are four of us.

632
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:58,619
Let's play eight-ball.

633
00:36:03,059 --> 00:36:03,860
Ms. Miao, do you know how to play?

634
00:36:19,039 --> 00:36:21,019
Chen Yi took the heat for me this time.

635
00:36:22,079 --> 00:36:23,219
You two helped me a lot

636
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:25,400
with the Sun Hu situation.

637
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,559
Thanks.

638
00:36:30,179 --> 00:36:30,940
He was

639
00:36:30,940 --> 00:36:32,260
after me anyway.

640
00:36:34,659 --> 00:36:35,460
He's probably still bitter

641
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:36,199
about what happened

642
00:36:36,199 --> 00:36:36,980
with Mr. Zhai.

643
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:40,940
You've shown him

644
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,320
a lot of respect.

645
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,659
Mr. Zhang, you were so invested

646
00:36:47,659 --> 00:36:48,619
in the new route before.

647
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:51,079
Now that Sun Hu's messed it up,

648
00:36:52,059 --> 00:36:53,159
you must have a backup plan, right?

649
00:36:54,139 --> 00:36:54,619
Is that so?

650
00:36:58,219 --> 00:36:58,900
Those routes

651
00:36:58,900 --> 00:37:00,119
