652
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,820
A lot of paperwork needs to be redone.

653
00:37:03,380 --> 00:37:04,599
But the client orders

654
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:05,599
can't be delayed.

655
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:07,639
As for

656
00:37:08,739 --> 00:37:09,599
other options...

657
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,820
As for other options,

658
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,320
it all depends on Yi.

659
00:37:15,539 --> 00:37:16,280
Like

660
00:37:16,559 --> 00:37:17,780
that arson last time.

661
00:37:18,659 --> 00:37:19,639
It was risky,

662
00:37:20,780 --> 00:37:21,219
but compared to

663
00:37:21,219 --> 00:37:22,719
what he went through in Jinguo,

664
00:37:22,719 --> 00:37:23,980
