665
00:37:26,539 --> 00:37:27,280
Jinguo?

666
00:37:28,119 --> 00:37:29,139
You've been to Jinguo?

667
00:37:29,639 --> 00:37:31,039
Mr. Zhang, you sank it.

668
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,059
I forgot.

669
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,940
The eight-ball went in.

670
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:02,679
Only thinking about the eight ball?

671
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,360
Chen Yi,

672
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,579
