673
00:38:08,239 --> 00:38:08,840
Want another round?

674
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,420
Maybe not.

675
00:38:10,679 --> 00:38:11,719
We've got other things to do.

676
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:12,559
I'm leaving.

677
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:16,659
Mr. Zhang,

678
00:38:17,119 --> 00:38:17,719
I'm heading out too.

679
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:18,920
Alright.

680
00:38:20,559 --> 00:38:21,760
I'll have Li drive you.

681
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,599
A few years ago, he was barely an adult.

682
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:33,539
A kid

683
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,340
