684
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,280
Never thought

685
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,760
I'd get my chance to turn it around.

686
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:41,340
You know

687
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:42,800
why he lost today?

688
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,920
People let up

689
00:38:48,239 --> 00:38:49,099
and they regress.

690
00:38:50,179 --> 00:38:51,360
He doesn't need to

691
00:38:51,719 --> 00:38:53,400
hustle pool for a living anymore.

692
00:38:58,780 --> 00:39:00,119
Back then,

693
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:01,099
