694
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:03,059
had nothing to lose,

695
00:39:03,739 --> 00:39:04,900
so he had nothing to fear.

696
00:39:05,719 --> 00:39:07,159
But now it's different.

697
00:39:08,139 --> 00:39:09,559
Now he has things he cares about

698
00:39:09,559 --> 00:39:10,599
and people he values.

699
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,079
So he can't

700
00:39:14,079 --> 00:39:14,940
stay completely focused.

701
00:39:17,940 --> 00:39:18,659
You know how it is.

702
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,099
When a player

703
00:39:22,239 --> 00:39:23,260
steps up to the table,

704
00:39:23,559 --> 00:39:24,320
where every ball ends up

705
00:39:24,340 --> 00:39:25,659
and which pocket

706
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:26,599
it goes into

707
00:39:27,579 --> 00:39:28,880
have to be crystal clear

708
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:29,840
in his mind.

709
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,320
So,

710
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,699
to be completely focused,

711
00:39:43,179 --> 00:39:43,920
