716
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,980
Can't you just be honest?

717
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:04,860
Miao Jing.

718
00:40:05,179 --> 00:40:06,179
I don't want to talk to you.

719
00:40:48,659 --> 00:40:49,760
Why are you back so late?

720
00:41:00,739 --> 00:41:02,239
Whatever Zhou Kang'an says, you listen.

721
00:41:02,619 --> 00:41:03,420
You sure follow orders.

722
00:41:04,659 --> 00:41:05,340
Stand still.

723
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:11,019
It's good to shake off the bad luck.

724
00:41:11,199 --> 00:41:11,800
Might have to

725
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,380
go see him a few more times.

726
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,500
He probably wants someone else, not me.

727
00:41:18,599 --> 00:41:19,659
Better not.

728
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,539
If you want to wade into this mess,

729
00:41:24,780 --> 00:41:25,800
I can't stop you.

730
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:31,579
I can stir the water,

731
00:41:32,679 --> 00:41:33,960
