732
00:41:39,199 --> 00:41:39,920
Do you trust me?

733
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:43,559
I do.

734
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:47,480
But we both have to

735
00:41:47,480 --> 00:41:48,400
