738
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:05,340
Don't hit my head.

739
00:42:05,900 --> 00:42:06,440
What?

740
00:42:06,719 --> 00:42:07,739
I said don't hit my head.

741
00:43:52,179 --> 00:43:52,619
What's going on?

742
00:43:52,619 --> 00:43:53,579
I haven't saved my work.

743
00:43:53,579 --> 00:43:54,460
Me neither.

744
00:43:54,460 --> 00:43:54,960
What do we do?

745
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:55,780
Did we just lose all our work?

746
00:43:55,780 --> 00:43:56,420
That's weird.

747
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:57,760
I still have a form to submit.

748
00:43:58,079 --> 00:43:59,340
Think it's bad luck? Like a jinx?

749
00:44:02,579 --> 00:44:03,179
Your zodiac year

750
00:44:03,179 --> 00:44:04,219
was ages ago.

751
00:44:04,219 --> 00:44:05,159
Still blaming it on that?

752
00:44:06,880 --> 00:44:08,940
In Vineton, they say go with the flow.

753
00:44:09,460 --> 00:44:11,059
Might as well enjoy this paid break.
